com.onfleet.demo.homework.struct

Class Location

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.onfleet.demo.homework.struct.Location
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    @Immutable
public final class Location
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Specifies location information for a Task, which may be assigned to a Driver. A location carries with it a pair of geo-coordinates.
    See Also:
